Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.46,0:00:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咖啡續杯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有件事想拜託折木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.78,0:00:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎？拜託？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.17,0:00:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實這是我的個人問題 我沒有拜託您的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.63,0:00:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之能先聽我道來詳情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好吧…只是聽聽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的
